  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nOn Mac, the top-level \"Tab\" menu includes an item that allows tabs to be added to a group. That menu item is enabled for all windows except app windows. If the user adds an undocked DevTools tab to a group, an extension can then move the tab to another window and trigger"
